Remarks

This object implements functions from libmpv's client.h that accept mpvHandle

Constructors

MPVClient(nint?, string?, bool)

Construct MPVClient

public MPVClient(nint? handle = null, string? name = null, bool weak = false)

Parameters

handle nint?

Optional handle to create client for the same player core

name string

Optional unique client name

weak bool

Whether the new client should be weak or not. If true, the created handle is treated as a weak reference. If all handles referencing a core are weak references, the core is automatically destroyed.

Exceptions

Exception

Thrown if failed to create mpvHandle

Properties

MPV client handle

public nint Handle { get; init; }

Id
